{
  "texts": [
    "A necessary requirement for a functioning certification system is that the certifier can assess at least ex-post the safety features of the AI-based system.",
    "With ex-ante assessment, the certifier assigns the safety class to the AI-based system.",
    "When the certifier can only assess ex-post, the party in control of the AI-based system self-declares the safety class.",
    "It has to compensate the certifier in case misclassification is detected ex-post.",
    "In either case, users make claims against the certifier, and thus the certifier becomes liable."
  ]
}